{
  "stem": "2578.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to bring it from, from other places.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was the normal times of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I would say that, after the second-- I would say, after, after the second winter in the ghetto, you wouldn't find one piece of wooden furniture standing in good order.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because everything was chopped up, in order to heat the rooms in the winter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Forget about coal or, or wood to, to, to warm the houses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't have it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, coming back to May 8th, after the Germans left, about 10 o'clock in the morning, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a civilian Russian car drove into the camp.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Germans, of course, were gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The gates were open.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And two German-- I'm sorry, two Russian officers jump out of the car, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with machine guns in their hands, and looking around, not realizing what it is.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then they saw the faces, staring out from the paneless windows.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because the windows-- the windows in that barrack that we were we didn't have any, any, any glass, just open, open holes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they saw these faces.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They realized what it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They called us out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So those who were capable of walking out came out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they surrounded this car.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "One of the officers got on the roof of the car.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he spoke to us, naturally, in Russian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And, since some of the inmates knew Russian, or at least part of it-- Because, don't forget, there were elderly Jews, who still remembered the Russians from the, the First World War.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they lived under the Russian-- under the Russian occupation under the Czar.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they knew a certain amount of Russian.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
